name: __ECommonUserInitializationState
doc: Enum describing the state of initialization for a specific user

Unknown: User has not started login process
DoingInitialLogin: Player is in the process of acquiring a user id with local login
DoingNetworkLogin: Player is performing the network login, they have already logged in locally
FailedtoLogin: Player failed to log in at all
LoggedInOnline: Player is logged in and has access to online functionality
LoggedInLocalOnly: Player is logged in locally (either guest or real user), but cannot perform online actions
